  <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-12">
    <!-- Professional Summary -->
    <section class="animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">About</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Graduate student at Cal Poly, San Luis Obispo pursuing an MS in Business Analytics.
        Specializing in machine learning, statistical theory, and building AI-powered tools.
        Passionate about applying data science to solve real-world problems and creating
